result.name: Cafe Fresca

reviews.text: Great coffee Chill Vibe

Home made bread, great coffee, super fresh ingredients, good service and great prices. This is one of the better cafes in Hong Kong.
Highly recommend the butter cookies.
Ordered 5 coffees... Americano, Cafe latte n cappuccino... Barrister did a good job on all 5 coffee.  Hot, smooth & aromatic! We enjoy it very much! Thanks 👍👍
Had two ciabatta sandwiches. Extremely fresh and good quality ingredients at great prices. Will definitely come again!!
Great cafe with really tasty food and a lovely atmosphere. 100% recommend.

result.name: Ho Man Tin Public Transport Interchange

reviews.text: Ho Man Tin MTR Station is not in Quarry Hill. It's over at the south end of Ho Man Tin bordering Hung Hom at Chatham Road North, next to Polyuniversity.
Well done.
搞清楚「何文田邨公共運輸交匯處」係位於常富街近景文樓，並不是忠孝街「港鐵何文田站 A3 出口巴士站」，呢度好多圖片都搞錯。
雖然由何文田站去好多何文田既地方都好遠，但是有選擇點都好過冇選擇既......
地鐵站太遠了。在何文田街都是坐巴士放便。
